</li></ul></li><li> Inverted in the <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/Dune" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/Dune">Dune</a></em> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FilmOfTheBook" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FilmOfTheBook">Film of the Book</a> (2000 version), where <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> Rabban</span> does this when he <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhCrap" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/OhCrap">realizes</a> that <em>he</em> is about to become the metaphorical ex-beloved ally.
