</li></ul></div>
<p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder10');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Western Animation&nbsp;</div><div id="folder10" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;">
<ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/VoltronLegendaryDefender" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/VoltronLegendaryDefender">Voltron: Legendary Defender</a></em>: In "Reunion", Pidge lets out a wail when <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">she believes her brother Matt to be dead when she sees a marker for him at a mass grave</span>.
