<h2 class="bold font-l">Ariandel's Rage</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When the player downs Sister Friede, Father Ariandel uncovers his eyes and witnesses her body. He enters a scream of rage and goes berserk. </p>
</div>
